- Static members can only access static members and not otehrs.
- Associated with class itself.


Syntax:
-------
private static int allPassengers; //Total across multiple instances.

Flight.getAllPassengers();


Static imports:
----------------
- Used with static methods
- Allows method name to be used without being class-qualified

import static  com.....Flight.resetAllPassengers;
import static  com.....Flight.*;



Static initilization block:-
----------------------------
- perform one-time type initilization
- Execute before type's first use.

static{ //Initilized only once when this class starts
   Put something int he map that was Initilized as a member

}
